flowchart TD
    A([User opens /window-compare]) --> B{Choose comparison type}
    B --> C[Select a Preset]
    B --> D[Enter custom date/time ranges]

    C --> E[Preset: Yesterday vs Today\nor Last Week Same Time]
    D --> F[Window A: Baseline\nstart + end datetime]
    D --> G[Window B: Current\nstart + end datetime]

    E --> H[Submit to /window-compare/result]
    F --> H
    G --> H

    H --> I[GET /api/window-compare/compare\nwith ISO-8601 parameters]

    I --> J[(pgconsole schema\nhistory tables)]

    J --> K[Aggregate samples\nfor Window A]
    J --> L[Aggregate samples\nfor Window B]

    K --> M[Compute deltas\nand change %]
    L --> M

    M --> N[Match queries by query_id\nbetween windows]

    N --> O{Query status}
    O --> P[New: appeared in Window B only]
    O --> Q[Gone: disappeared from Window B]
    O --> R[Regression: mean_time increased > threshold]
    O --> S[OK: within acceptable range]

    M --> T[Overall direction badge\nImproved / Degraded / Mixed]
    P --> U([Result page rendered])
    Q --> U
    R --> U
    S --> U
    T --> U
